  "bookPageHeroTitle": "From first idea to finished book",
  "bookPageHeroSubtitle": "Turn your expertise into a beautiful, professionally published book. Stonechat guides you from brainstorming and writing to design, printing, and launch.",
  "bookStartProjectCta": "Start your book project",
  "bookServicesOverline": "Book services",
  "bookServicesTitle": "Everything you need to publish with confidence",
  "bookServicesIntro": "Whether you are starting with a rough idea, a draft manuscript, or a finished book that needs design and printing, Stonechat offers an end-to-end publication service tailored to busy leaders and experts.",
  "bookSvc1Title": "Book strategy & structure",
  "bookSvc1Body": "Clarify your core message, define who the book is for, and shape your ideas into a clear chapter outline. We help you decide what belongs in the book and what can stay out, so writing becomes faster and more focused.",
  "bookSvc1Highlight": "Ideal for leaders and experts who know what they want to say but are not sure how to organise it.",
  "bookSvc2Title": "Writing, editing & translation",
  "bookSvc2Body": "Through interviews, co-writing and careful editing, we turn your knowledge into polished, publication-ready chapters. Our editorial team writes in your voice in both English and Khmer, then refines every page for accuracy and flow.",
  "bookSvc2Highlight": "You stay the author and decision-maker; we do the heavy lifting on the page from first draft to final proof.",
  "bookSvc3Title": "Design, layout & publishing",
  "bookSvc3Body": "We create a professional cover, design clean interior pages, and prepare all print and digital files your printer needs. Our team coordinates specifications, quotations and test prints so your finished books look world-class on every shelf.",
  "bookSvc3Highlight": "One partner from design concept to printed books in your hands, ready for launch.",
  "bookProcessTitle": "How your book comes to life",
  "bookProcessSubtitle": "A single, guided process from first conversation to printed books in your hands.",
  "bookProcessStep1Title": "1. Discovery & brainstorming",
  "bookProcessStep1Body": "We explore your story, goals, audience, and timeline, then shape them into a clear book concept and working outline.",
  "bookProcessStep2Title": "2. Writing & editorial",
  "bookProcessStep2Body": "Through interviews, draft reviews, and editorial passes, we co-create chapters that sound like you and read like a pro.",
  "bookProcessStep3Title": "3. Design & production",
  "bookProcessStep3Body": "We design the cover, lay out the pages, prepare print and digital files, and manage printers to agreed quality standards.",
  "bookProcessStep4Title": "4. Launch & beyond",
  "bookProcessStep4Body": "You receive finished books and launch materials; we can also support events, media, and social content to amplify impact.",
  "bookPricingHeading": "Transparent packages, customised to your book",
  "bookPricingIntro": "Every project begins with a conversation. These packages give you a clear starting point — we then tailor scope, timelines and print quantities to match your goals and budget.",
  "bookPlanAuthorStarterName": "Author Starter",
  "bookPlanAuthorStarterStrapline": "Ideal if you already have a draft or detailed notes.",
  "bookPlanAuthorStarterBullet1": "Book concept and chapter outline workshop",
  "bookPlanAuthorStarterBullet2": "Editorial review of manuscript (up to 40,000 words)",
  "bookPlanAuthorStarterBullet3": "Line editing and proofreading",
  "bookPlanAuthorStarterBullet4": "Simple interior layout and print-ready files",
  "bookPlanSignatureName": "Signature Book",
  "bookPlanSignatureStrapline": "Our most popular end-to-end package for leaders and experts.",
  "bookPlanSignatureBullet1": "Strategy, positioning and full chapter outline",
  "bookPlanSignatureBullet2": "Ghostwriting or co-writing based on interviews",
  "bookPlanSignatureBullet3": "Professional editing, proofreading and fact-checking",
  "bookPlanSignatureBullet4": "Custom cover design and premium interior layout",
  "bookPlanSignatureBullet5": "Print coordination (recommended specs and quotations)",
  "bookPlanLaunchLegacyName": "Launch & Legacy",
  "bookPlanLaunchLegacyStrapline": "For books that anchor your brand, organisation or campaign.",
  "bookPlanLaunchLegacyBullet1": "Everything in Signature Book",
  "bookPlanLaunchLegacyBullet2": "Launch event and media talking points pack",
  "bookPlanLaunchLegacyBullet3": "Social media launch kit (posts, visuals, captions)",
