  "appsPageDevHeroTitle": "From idea to App Store and Play Store",
  "appsPageDevHeroSubtitle": "Turn your vision into a polished mobile or web app. Stonechat guides you from concept and design through development, testing, and submission to the App Store and Google Play.",
  "appsStartProjectCta": "Start your app project",
  "appsServicesOverline": "App services",
  "appsServicesTitle": "Everything you need to ship a great app",
  "appsServicesIntro": "Whether you need a simple MVP or a full-featured product, Stonechat delivers end-to-end app development. We work with startups, enterprises, and organisations who want to move fast without cutting corners.",
  "appSvc1Title": "Strategy & discovery",
  "appSvc1Body": "We clarify your app idea, define core features, and map user flows. Together we decide what to build first so you launch faster and stay within budget.",
  "appSvc1Highlight": "Ideal when you have a vision but need a clear roadmap to execute it.",
  "appSvc2Title": "Design & development",
  "appSvc2Body": "Our team designs intuitive interfaces and builds native or cross-platform apps for iOS, Android, and web. We use modern stacks and follow best practices for performance and security.",
  "appSvc2Highlight": "You get a production-ready app that feels fast and looks professional.",
  "appSvc3Title": "Testing & store submission",
  "appSvc3Body": "We test on real devices, fix bugs, and handle App Store and Google Play submission. From screenshots and descriptions to compliance checks, we get your app live.",
  "appSvc3Highlight": "One partner from final build to published app in both stores.",
  "appProcessTitle": "How your app gets built and published",
